Description¶

Orange-county-letting’s is a start-up in the real estate rental industry. It is an OpenClassrooms project whose goal is to scale an existing application using a modular architecture. Link to the original project: https://github.com/OpenClassrooms-Student-Center/Python-OC-Lettings-FR
